## 📋 Project overview

**"Beyond writing code: orchestrating AI agents as engineering infrastructure"**

Going beyond asking AI for code snippets, I practice the **Agentic Development Paradigm** — where AI agents fully grasp project context and autonomously execute complex engineering tasks. I've built and operated a proprietary AI infrastructure that combines centralized configuration management with precision-designed project directives.

<ProjectTechStack techStack={metadata.techStack} {locale} />

## ⚙️ Key work

